# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository. This keeps Windows and
# Linux/WSL clones consistent without any per-machine git config, and travels
# with the repo (CI included). Working copies are checked out as LF on every
# platform; set `core.autocrlf=true` locally if you want CRLF working copies on
# Windows.
* text=auto

# Binary assets — never apply EOL conversion.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.tga  binary
*.pdn  binary
